text: Spinachitina is an extinct genus of chitinozoans. It was described by Schallreuter in 1963.Spinachitina at ChitDB: Chitinozoans of Baltica. ==Species== * Spinachitina cervicornis (Eisenack, 1931) * Spinachitina coronata (Eisenack, 1931) * Spinachitina fragilis (Nestor, 1980) * Spinachitina maennili (Nestor, 1980) * Spinachitina multiradiata (Eisenack, 1959) * Spinachitina suecica (Laufeld, 1967) * Spinachitina taugourdeaui (Eisenack, 1968) * Spinachitina tvaerensis Grahn, Nõlvak et Paris, 1996 ==References== Category:Prehistoric marine animals Category:Fossil taxa described in 1963
title: Spinachitina
